## Matrix Operations

### Basic Operations Notation

<CodeGroup>
```latex matrix-operations.tex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\begin{document}

% Matrix multiplication
$AB = \begin{pmatrix}
a & b \\
c & d
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
e & f \\
g & h
\end{pmatrix}
= \begin{pmatrix}
ae + bg & af + bh \\
ce + dg & cf + dh
\end{pmatrix}$

% Transpose
$A^T = \begin{pmatrix}
1 & 2 & 3 \\
4 & 5 & 6
\end{pmatrix}^T
= \begin{pmatrix}
1 & 4 \\
2 & 5 \\
3 & 6
\end{pmatrix}$

% Inverse (2×2 formula)
$A^{-1} = \begin{pmatrix}
a & b \\
c & d
\end{pmatrix}^{-1}
= \frac{1}{ad-bc}
\begin{pmatrix}
d & -b \\
-c & a
\end{pmatrix}$

% Matrix power
$A^2 = AA = \begin{pmatrix}
1 & 2 \\
3 & 4
\end{pmatrix}^2
= \begin{pmatrix}
7 & 10 \\
15 & 22
\end{pmatrix}$

\end{document}
```
